### Guardar almacén

POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/almacen
Authorization: Bearer 2|2moXMJ1eM3zTsGkJVtJfOEUu52CtpP5tjDq4UNMpef4da40b
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
"nombre": "Almacén Central",
"descripcion": "Almacén principal de distribución",
"codigo": "ALM-MAIN-01",
"sucursal_id": 1
}

